      "comment": "WILD MONARCH (4) two-year-old Wild Ruler gelding out of Homebird on debut for the Jenny Graham yard. Looked strong in his only trial when second over 1006m at Port Macquarie. Maps well and expected to go close. WEOWNACHEVY (3) Winning Rupert gelding from Kitty Cotswold on debut for the Andrew Parramore stable. Has a total of three trials leading into this. Gets his chance in a fairly open contest. SUBSIDING (7) Harry Angel filly from the good producing mare Diminish on debut for the Matt Dunn yard. Has looked sharp in her two trials and capable of taking this out. WHY WAIT (9) Anders filly from Why're You Waiting on debut for the Matt Dunn stable. Fitted with the two trials and gets every chance from the inside draw. ASHKIRK (1) Ole Kirk gelding out of Hams Al Lail on debut for the Matt Dunn yard. Has looked okay in two trials and place claims best from the wide gate.",
